snippet.title: StuntBoost - Official Gameplay Trailer | The MIX Fall Showcase 2024
snippet.description: Get a deep dive into the gameplay of StuntBoost in this latest trailer for the upcoming game. In StuntBoost, grab your finger-skateboard and race against time on tiny tracks of cardboard and toys. Discover shortcuts, perform stunts, manipulate gravity, and take advantage of your environment to reach the goal as fast as possible in this celebration of speed. StuntBoost will be available on PC.
